# 

 
 # 题目背景 
<p>NOIP2016提高组</p> 

 
 # 题目描述 
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">小南有一套可爱的玩具小人,&nbsp;它们各有不同的职业。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">有一天,&nbsp;这些玩具小人把小南的眼镜藏了起来。&nbsp;小南发现玩具小人们围成了一个圈,它们有的面朝圈内,有的面朝圈外。如下图:</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 388px; height: 300px;" /></p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">这时singer告诉小南一个谜題:&nbsp;&ldquo;眼镜藏在我左数第3个玩具小人的右数第1个玩具小人的左数第2个玩具小人那里。&nbsp;&rdquo;</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">小南发现,&nbsp;这个谜题中玩具小人的朝向非常关键,&nbsp;因为朝内和朝外的玩具小人的左右方向是相反的:&nbsp;面朝圈内的玩具小人,&nbsp;它的左边是顺时针方向,&nbsp;右边是逆时针方向;&nbsp;而面向圈外的玩具小人,&nbsp;它的左边是逆时针方向,&nbsp;右边是顺时针方向。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">小南一边艰难地辨认着玩具小人,&nbsp;一边数着:</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">singer朝内,&nbsp;左数第3个是archer。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">archer朝外,右数第1个是thinker。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">thinker朝外,&nbsp;左数第2个是writer。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">所以眼镜藏在writer这里!</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">虽然成功找回了眼镜,&nbsp;但小南并没有放心。&nbsp;如果下次有更多的玩具小人藏他的眼镜,&nbsp;或是谜題的长度更长,&nbsp;他可能就无法找到眼镜了&nbsp;。&nbsp;所以小南希望你写程序帮他解决类似的谜題。&nbsp;这样的谜題具体可以描述为:</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">有&nbsp;n个玩具小人围成一圈,&nbsp;已知它们的职业和朝向。现在第1个玩具小人告诉小南一个包含&nbsp;m条指令的谜題,&nbsp;其中第&nbsp;z条指令形如&ldquo;左数/右数第&nbsp;s,个玩具小人&rdquo;。&nbsp;你需要输出依次数完这些指令后,到达的玩具小人的职业。</p> 

 
 # 输入格式 
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">输入的第一行包含西个正整数&nbsp;n,m,&nbsp;表示玩具小人的个数和指令的条数。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">接下来&nbsp;n行,&nbsp;每行包含一个整数和一个字符串,&nbsp;以逆时针为顺序给出每个玩具小人的朝向和职业。其中0表示朝向圈内,&nbsp;1表示朝向圈外。保证不会出现其他的数。字符串长度不超过10且仅由小写字母构成,&nbsp;字符串不为空,&nbsp;并且字符串两两不同。&nbsp;整数和字符串之问用一个空格隔开。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">接下来&nbsp;m行,其中第&nbsp;z行包含两个整数&nbsp;a,,s,,表示第&nbsp;z条指令。若&nbsp;a,=&nbsp;0,表示向左数&nbsp;s,个人;若a,=&nbsp;1&nbsp;,表示向右数&nbsp;s,个人。保证a,不会出现其他的数,&nbsp;1&le;&nbsp;s,&lt;n&nbsp;。</p> 

 
 # 输出格式 
<p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">输出一个字符串,&nbsp;表示从第一个读入的小人开始,&nbsp;依次数完&nbsp;m条指令后到达的小人的职业。</span></p>
